dc_title_s: Insurance maps of Minneapolis, Minnesota, last revised 1930, Volume 7
dc_description_s: Updated with pasteover slips and additional sheets. Date of last revision varies between 1924-1930. Each volume includes a map of ward lines and district lines and a volume boundary map (index map to all volumes). Columbia Heights and Fridley, Anoka County, are shown in Volume Seven.|v.7: sheets 751-863|70 Centimeters|Scale 1:600. 50 feet to 1 inch|City of Minneapolis Archives
